data.description: Stunning lake front home prime lot, enjoy breathe taking sunsets from screened in porch. This home features 3bdrm 2 bath 2 car garage with no carpet all tile throughout. For added safety, accordion shutters are installed, barrel roof adds a touch of elegance. Furniture negotiable ready to move in. This stunning home in Bent Creek community is gated back entrance exclusively for residents, community pool, fitness ctr., basketball court and a park. Located 7 minutes away from downtown shops, marina, close to Fort Pierce beautiful beaches and more
